Interface AttributeListInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
AttributeList
public interface AttributeListInterface

Interface for AttributeList objects.

Outlines the generic methods that must be present in all AttributeList objects.

Version:
1.0
Author:
David Kong, Queen's University, August 2002.
